Package com.sudoplay.axion.adapter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RegistryAccessor
    The RegistryAccessor class holds a reference to a TagRegistry and allows sub-classes read-only access to the registry.
    TagAdapter<T extends Tag>
    Classes that extend the abstract TagAdapter class define how Tags are read from and written to the underlying streams.
    TagAdapter.Ext
    Group of TagAdapters that conform to Axion's custom, extended specification.
    TagAdapter.Spec
    Group of TagAdapters that conform to the original NBT specification.
    TagConverter<T extends Tag,V>
    Classes that extend the abstract TagConverter class define how Tags are converted to and from their respective values.
    TagConverter.Ext
    Group of TagConverters that conform to Axion's custom, extended specification.
    TagConverter.Spec
    Group of TagConverters that conform to the original NBT specification.
    TagRegistry
    The TagRegistry class is responsible for maintaining relationships between integer ids, Tag classes, Tag value classes, TagAdapters, and TagConverters and providing lookup methods to access the data via its relationships.

    Exception Description
    AxionTagRegistrationException
